<HEAD>Roh Appeals To North Korea To Take Part In Olympics</HEAD>
<NOTE>Eds: Subs 5th graf pvs ``Less than...'' with one graf to CORRECT
that press photographers hit, sted detained. Pickup 6th graf pvs
