<HEAD>Dole Attacks Bush With Iran-Contra Ads</HEAD>
<NOTE>Eds: Updates with Gephardt-Carter meeting, inserting new grafs
3-4, and subbing 1 graf for grafs 8-9 pvs, One Southern ...
Democratic caucuses.</NOTE>
<BYLINE>By LAURA KING</BYLINE>
