 <PERSON> Michael </PERSON> <PERSON> Dukakis </PERSON> won the <LOCATION> Vermont </LOCATION> Democratic presidential primary on Tuesday, with <PERSON> Jesse </PERSON> <PERSON> Jackson </PERSON> running second. It was the <LOCATION> Massachusetts </LOCATION> governor's third <LOCATION> New </LOCATION> <LOCATION> England </LOCATION> victory, following <LOCATION> New </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Hampshire </LOCATION> and <LOCATION> Maine </LOCATION>.
